 * NOTE   = (A  | B | C | D | E | F | G) [ACC] [NUMBER] | R
 * ACC    = # | s | b 
 * TYPE   = MAJ | M | MIN | m | ...
 * CHORD  = NOTE [TYPE] [/ NUMBER] | {NOTE [, NOTE]}
 * SONG   = CHORDS+
 * 
 * Example: Cadd9/2 
 * @param {*} text 
